==English==
=== Etymology ===
From [[physicist]] [[Peltier|John C. A. Peltier]] the [[discoverer]] of the effect

=== Noun ===
'''Peltier effect'''
# ([[Physics]]) a [[thermodynamic]] effect which occurs when current is passed through a [[thermocouple]], used in [[computing]] as a cooling process

